    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hydrographic features, including grounds, banks, or other watery areas, where fishermen go to catch fish. For places on land where fishermen gather, use "fishing spots."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
